text: Pinkfong is a South Korean children's educational branch. It started as an application produced by The Pinkfong Company, and has since advanced into various fields such as nursery rhymes, musicals, games, and animation. The "Pinkfong Baby Shark - Kids' Songs & Stories" Youtube channel was launched on 13 December 2011. == Related pages == * Baby Shark * Pinkfong Wonderstar * Go, Dog.
